name: JUMP YOUR WAY THROUGH
description:
I am a 10 year old kid who recently started programming.This game is for Miz Jam 1 and this is platformer where you have to destroy the boss at the end to win(also there are a lot of incomplete things)Pls Try.

Please send feedback because this is my first time submitting  a game!

Arrow keys to move 

Space bar to jump press space bar twice to double jump
